data.description: The perfect place to call home in a quiet neighborhood close to Grand Canyon University. Come see this home that was completely remodeled in 2021 with new flooring, gorgeous kitchen, and bathrooms with all the bells and whistles. The backyard is big, and this property is has everything you want in a home. Motivated seller is offering $10,000 towards closing costs or rate buy down.
